== Relationals bind tighter than logical operators (NOT the Pascal mistake):
== 'A < B and C < D' parses as '(A < B) and (C < D)' with no parentheses needed.

Module PrecedenceRelationalLogical

Main :
    A := 1
    B := 2
    C := 3
    D := 4
    R := A < B and C < D
    PutLn(R)
;
